flowchart TD
    A[IOCs Schema] --> B[reports: array]
    B --> C[report item: object]

    C --> C0[metadata: object]
    C0 --> M1[url: string, uri]
    C0 --> M2[created: string, DD/MM/YYYY]
    C0 --> M3[severity: low/medium/high/critical]
    C0 --> M4[confidence: low/medium/high]
    C0 --> M5[tags: array optional]
    C --> C1[iocs: array]
    C --> C2[vulns: array optional]
    C --> C3[ttps: array]
    C --> C4[queries: array optional]
    C --> C5[xrefs: array optional]

    R0[Required report fields: metadata, iocs, ttps] --> C

    C1 --> I1[ioc item: object]
    I1 --> I2[id: string]
    I1 --> I3[type: enum]
    I1 --> I4[malign: boolean]
    I1 --> I5[hash: sha1/sha256/md5 optional for file]
    I1 --> I6[cert_serial: optional for file/domain/ip]
    I1 --> I7[value: string]
    I1 --> I8[comment: string optional]
    R1[Required IOC fields: id, type, malign, value] --> I1
    I3 --> IT1[email]
    I3 --> IT2[ip]
    I3 --> IT3[domain]
    I3 --> IT4[url]
    I3 --> IT5[file]
    I3 --> IT6[process]
    I3 --> IT7[cmdline]

    C2 --> V1[vuln item: object]
    V1 --> V2[id: CVE-YYYY-NNNN]
    V1 --> V3[comment: string]
    R2[Required vuln fields: id, comment] --> V1

    C3 --> T1[ttp item: object]
    T1 --> T2[id: TXXXX or TXXXX.XXX]
    T1 --> T3[comment: string]
    R3[Required TTP fields: id, comment] --> T1

    C4 --> Q1[query item: object]
    Q1 --> Q2[id: query-N]
    Q1 --> Q3[type: kql/yara/spl/sigma/sql]
    Q1 --> Q4[value: string]
    Q1 --> Q5[iocs: array optional]
    Q1 --> Q6[ttps: array optional]
    Q1 --> Q7[comment: string optional]
    R4[Required query fields: id, type, value] --> Q1

    C5 --> X1[xref item: object]
    X1 --> X2[id: string]
    X1 --> X3[type: creates/uses]
    X1 --> X4[from: array optional refs]
    X1 --> X5[to: array optional refs]
    X1 --> X6[comment: string optional]
    R5[Required xref fields: id, type] --> X1